==English==

===Etymology===
From {{etyl|la}} {{term|dies|diēs|day|lang=la}} and {{term|malus||bad|lang=la}} ("bad day").

===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|/ˈdɪzm(ə)l/}}

===Adjective===
